    "greetingTitle": {
      "id": "Tagline \"MA MAFDA BESTARI\"",
      "en": "Tagline \"MA MAFDA BESTARI\""
    },
    "greetingBody": {
      "id": "Madrasah Aliyah Mafatihul Huda Cipari (MA MAFDA)  berkomitmen untuk menjadi lembaga pendidikan Islam yang unggul dan berkarakter. Melalui tagline BESTARI (Belajar, Berprestasi, dan Menginspirasi), kami bertekad menanamkan semangat belajar sepanjang hayat, menumbuhkan prestasi akademik dan non-akademik, serta membentuk generasi yang mampu memberi inspirasi bagi masyarakat.",
      "en": "Madrasah Aliyah Mafatihul Huda Cipari (MA MAFDA) is committed to becoming an outstanding Islamic educational institution grounded in strong character. Through the tagline BESTARI (Learning, Achieving, and Inspiring), we are dedicated to fostering a spirit of lifelong learning, cultivating academic and non-academic achievements, and shaping a generation capable of inspiring the community."
    },
